Class ListTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • ListTest

  • public class ListTest
extends java.lang.Object
    JUnit Tests class to test Lists by running several different scenarios as parameters and checking the output of each defined List function. Utilises hamcrest Matchers
    Author:
    lewispalmer
